::Zardus/Repressor::

Zardus nods at Lambda. "I might very soon, yes."

Before he could elaborate, he looks over at Gotron as the bot 
approaches with Jaws, nodding.

"Yes, I do," he says. He looks at Lanbda. "I might have a mission for 
you very soon. For now, I think you should get familiar with the 
base."

Zardus' eyes almost widen as he recieves Diamond's transmission. 
KitKat was dead? He glances down at his wrist comp to check. The Iron 
Fist returns an affirmative responce: it couldn't detect KitKat 
anywhere on the planet.

"Excellent job," his comm replies, nothing sounding externaly, "Get 
some rest. Did you have any trouble getting in?"

He was slightly curious as to how good the Predacon security was. 
Perhaps this war wouldn't be hard after all....
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Repressor looks at Feline as she approaches him, seeing her advances. 
That was one major programming fix...

"Er, Zardus is near the entrance to the base," he says, turning 
around to lead her to the Alliance commander.
